<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/771210-the-main-character-in-this-novel-is">The main character in this novel is Gabriel Noone. The last name suggests a link to the hero of the Greek tale of the cyclops. Was there any intention to make that allusion?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_771210'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F138180.The_Night_Listener">like</a></span>

</li>
